creator: UPSU
descriptionHtml:
Download the UPSU app to stay up to date with news, activities and opportunities for students at the University of Plymouth.

We’re here to make your time at Uni the best it can possible be and this app is your one stop shop for all things UPSU.
descriptionShort: The official student life app for the University of Plymouth Students’ Union.
